claim.claim-text:
12. A cargo bed assembly secured to and supported by a chassis of a motor vehicle, said cargo bed assembly comprising: 
a base extending between a front end and a back end and including a back support extending across said back end between a first end and a second end, each of said first and second ends fixedly secured to the chassis; 
a plurality of sidewalls fixedly secured to said base and perpendicular thereto; 
a plurality of spines fixedly secured to said back support and extending parallel to each other toward said front end of said base; and 
a brace fixedly secured to the chassis and engagable with said plurality of spines for absorbing torsional forces by twisting as the chassis transmits torsional forces to prevent said cargo bed assembly from bending and flexing.
